title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: The high expectations of others are likely only surpassed by your own personal standards. However, its a waste of time wondering if you can live up to their ideals when there are so many hills to climb. Doubt and fear only impede your growth rather than allowing you to reach your full potential. It doesnt mean you will fail in your mission if youre farther from your destination now than you wish. Thankfully, gently pushing yourself moves you forward without as much struggle. Michael Altshuler said, The bad news is time flies. The good news is youre the pilot. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
